== 1. Public Summary ==

FactHarbor is transitioning from a founder-led setup into a more formal Swiss-association structure.

Current public status:

* Verein founded on **23 April 2026**
* Commercial Register filing submitted on **27 April 2026**
* Entry letter received on **29 April 2026**
* UID / Firmennummer assigned: **CHE-448.446.098**

See [[Legal Framework>>FactHarbor.Organisation.Legal and Compliance.Legal Framework.WebHome]] for the current public legal-status summary.

== 2. Why The Detailed Plan Moved ==

The detailed transition page was moved out of the public repo tip because it contains:

* internal role-mapping details
* early-stage organisational transition assumptions
* founder-to-governance transition planning better kept in the private governance/admin track

